title: Ebro In The Morning - Discussing TERFs + Learning About Trans Issues
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/7/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the recent comments on trans issues made by Macy Gray and Bette Midler, and so much more! 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
